OL,3,CJury finds mother guilty of cruelty
OL,4,Cand murder of three-year-old son
OL,6,F* Warning - this article contains
OL,7,Fdistressing details about child
OL,8,Fcruelty and murder
OL,10,FA jury has found a mother guilty of
OL,11,Fmurdering her three-year-old son by
OL,12,Fshaking him so violently she caused a
OL,13,Ffatal brain injury.
OL,15,FChristina Robinson denied murdering
OL,16,Fher son Dwelaniyah Robinson at the
OL,17,Ffamily home in Bracken Court, Ushaw
OL,18,FMoor, Durham, in November 2022.
