OL,3,CJury finds mother guilty of cruelty
OL,4,Cand murder of three-year-old son
OL,6,FThe 30-year-old was also found guilty
OL,7,Fof four child cruelty offences, which
OL,8,Fhappened in the weeks leading up to
OL,9,Fhis death.
OL,11,FDuring the three-week trial at
OL,12,FNewcastle Crown Court, the prosecution
OL,13,Fset out how Robinson deliberately
OL,14,Fscalded the little boy as a
OL,15,Fpunishment, how she hit him with
OL,16,Fspoons, slapped him and beat him with
OL,17,Fa bamboo cane, how she did not seek
OL,18,Fmedical attention for his burns, and
OL,19,Fhow she neglected him by leaving him
OL,20,Falone at home.
