OL,6,FRobinson, who represented herself ,
OL,7,Ftold the jury in her closing speech on
OL,8,FTuesday 19 March: "Please do not find
OL,9,Fme guilty for something I have not
OL,10,Fdone."
OL,12,FBut on Thursday a jury found her
OL,13,Fguilty of all charges.
OL,15,FThe trial heard in the weeks prior to
OL,16,FDwelaniyah's, his mother had
OL,17,Fdeliberately immersed him in scalding
OL,18,Fwater, causing severe burns that would
OL,19,Fhave caused excruciating pain.
