OL,6,FShe treated his injuries herself and
OL,7,Fdid not seek medical help as
OL,8,Fsafeguarding concerns would have been
OL,9,Fobvious if a health worker saw him.
OL,11,FRobinson, a member of the Black Hebrew
OL,12,FIsraelite religion,
OL,14,FShe told Newcastle Crown Court her
OL,15,Freason to use the cane was that the
OL,16,Fyoungster was messing around with his
OL,17,Ffood.
