OL,6,FThe defendant, originally from
OL,7,FTamworth, Staffordshire, took more
OL,8,Fthan 20 minutes before dialling 999,
OL,9,Ffirst speaking to her husband on the
OL,10,Fphone despite him serving with the RAF
OL,11,F240 miles away, and then using Google
OL,12,Fto look at how to resuscitate a child.
OL,14,FWhen the emergency services arrived,
OL,15,FRobinson appeared calm as she
OL,16,Fexplained her version of events to a
OL,17,Fpolice officer while medics worked
OL,18,Fdesperately on Dwelaniyah.
