OL,6,FDespite their efforts at the scene
OL,7,FDwelaniyah could not be saved and
OL,8,Fprobably died at the house, although
OL,9,Ffurther attempts to resuscitate him
OL,10,Fwere made in hospital.
OL,12,FA post-mortem examination revealed he
OL,13,Fhad been the victim of a series of
OL,14,Fassaults and had sustained a number of
OL,15,Fnon-accidental injuries.
OL,17,FRichard Wright KC, prosecuting, said:
OL,18,F"In other words, somebody had been
OL,19,Fdeliberately hurting this little boy
OL,20,Fand had been doing so over a period of
OL,21,Ftime.
