OL,6,F"That person was his mother, the
OL,7,Fdefendant Christina Robinson."
OL,9,F'Campaign of violence for pretty
OL,10,Fwrongs'
OL,12,FIn his closing speech, Mr Wright told
OL,13,Fthe court: "He was subjected to a
OL,14,Fcampaign of violence and cruelty by
OL,15,Fhis mother for petty wrongs."
OL,17,FHer husband, Dwelaniyah's father,
OL,18,FGabriel Adu-Appau was away from the
OL,19,Ffamily home when his son was
OL,20,Frepeatedly injured.
