OL,6,FHe did not play any role in the trial.
OL,8,FHis wife was using a sperm donor to
OL,9,Ftry to conceive and, in October 2022,
OL,10,Fhad also made contact with a man named
OL,11,FChisom Innocent Onoja using a dating
OL,12,Fapp.
OL,14,FWhen she became pregnant, Robinson was
OL,15,Fin regular contact with health
OL,16,Fprofessionals, although she was not
OL,17,Fwilling to get treatment for her son's
OL,18,Finjuries.
