OL,6,FMr Justice Garnham will pass sentence
OL,7,Fon 24 May, giving time to the
OL,8,Fdefendant to seek legal representation
OL,9,Fafter she parted with her team just
OL,10,Fbefore the end of the trial.
OL,12,FHe thanked the jury, some of whom were
OL,13,Fvisibly upset, for their "obvious care
OL,14,Fand attention", and excused them from
OL,15,Ffurther service for 20 years.
OL,17,FThe judge said: "I know from looking
OL,18,Fat you, this has been a stressful
OL,19,Fprocess, you need to get away and do
OL,20,Fsomething else, and think about
OL,21,Fsomething more cheerful.
