OL,6,F"I am extremely grateful for all you
OL,7,Fhave done."
OL,9,F'A child's life is precious'
OL,11,FSpeaking after the verdict, Detective
OL,12,FChief Inspector Simon Turner, Senior
OL,13,FInvestigating Officer for Operation
OL,14,FAruana at Durham Constabulary, said
OL,15,FRobinson had created a web of lies to
OL,16,Fcover up her unnecessary violence.
