OL,6,F"A child's life is precious," he said.
OL,7,F"Dwelaniyah Robinson had his life
OL,8,Fsadly taken from him, at just three
OL,9,Fyears of age, having been beaten and
OL,10,Fabused at the hands of his own mother.
OL,12,F"She tragically subjected him to
OL,13,Frepeated lashings with a cane, and
OL,14,Fsubmerged him in scalding hot water,
OL,15,Fresulting in nearly 20 per cent burns.
OL,17,F"Even after this horrific abuse she
OL,18,Ffailed to seek treatment, leaving him
OL,19,Fin significant pain. Just weeks later
OL,20,Fwhilst still suffering, he was then
OL,21,Fsubject to a fatal head injury.
