OL,6,F"Christina Robinson lied from the
OL,7,Foutset, and I am pleased the jury has
OL,8,Fseen through her lies and convicted
OL,9,Fher today."
OL,11,FThis is the moment Durham Police
OL,12,Farrested Christina Robinson, initially
OL,13,Fon suspicion of neglect
