OL,16,Fhas been a truly horrific case, that
OL,17,Fhas affected everyone involved. I
OL,18,Fwould like to thank our investigation
OL,19,Fteam for their dedication and
OL,20,Fcommitment to get justice for
OL,21,FDwelaniyah.
