OL,6,F"My thoughts are with those who truly
OL,7,Fcared about Dwelaniyah. Sadly, nothing
OL,8,Fcan bring him back, but hopefully
OL,9,Ftoday's verdict will provide some
OL,10,Fclosure and allow them to grieve."
